title: GJFO & WRFO Boundary
name: GJFO & WRFO Boundary
description:
This data set consists of digital data describing BLM's Resource Area
Boundaries, also known as BLM Field Office Areas. These data
were derived from BLM Field Office data captured at 1:24,000. Data were then
mapjoined into a resulting statewide coverage. The coverage model was converted to a geodatabase.
Because of differences between
data capture techniques between BLM Offices the data editor droped some
boundaries from various Field Office Areas to avoid sliver problems. These
differences will be identified in the line attribute table within this geodatabase feature class.
See "Entity and Attribute Information" section for line source.
